// Week 11: Scaling and DAO Treasury Management
// Lecture: Managing funds and project growth
// Exploration: Mock voting on community funds for sensor purchases
#[account]
pub struct Treasury {
    pub total_funds: u64,
    pub proposals: Vec<Proposal>,
}

#[derive(Clone, AnchorSerialize, AnchorDeserialize)]
pub struct Proposal {
    pub description: String,
    pub requested_funds: u64,
    pub votes: u32,
}
**Week 11: DAO Treasury & Scaling Governance**
- **Lecture Topics:**
  - Treasury management on Solana
  - Managing group proposals
- **Exploration:**
  - Vote to allocate DAO treasury to purchase new sensors
  - Implement DAO budget proposal structure

```rust
#[derive(Accounts)]
pub struct SubmitProposal<'info> {
    #[account(mut)]
    pub dao_treasury: Account<'info, Treasury>,
    pub proposer: Signer<'info>,
    #[account(init, payer = proposer, space = 8 + Proposal::LEN)]
    pub proposal: Account<'info, Proposal>,
    pub system_program: Program<'info, System>,
}
